# Rule: Development Workflow

All contributions must adhere to the standards defined in `CONTRIBUTING.md`. Before completing a task, ensure the following:

-   Code is formatted with `black`.
-   Code passes all linter checks with `ruff`.
-   New features have both unit and integration tests written with `pytest`.
-   The "Definition of Done" checklist in the contributing guide has been met. 